    "type": "DecisionRecord",
    "actor": "https://uofa.net/morrison/actor/lead-credibility-assessor",
    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. Six factors appropriately scoped out per ASME V&V 40 Table 1 for MRL 2 assessment. Hemolysis index prediction error of 8.3% is within the 15% tolerance band. Worst-case operating point identification rate of 91.7% (11/12 conditions) is sufficient for the Class II device submission. The assessment team concludes that model credibility is established for the stated use.",
